thread.title: BRIEF-Probi Q1 Net Sales Fall To SEK 119.2 Million

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Probi Q1 Net Sales Fall To SEK 119.2 Million
text:
May 2 (Reuters) - Probi AB:
* Q1 NET SALES SEK 119.2 MILLION (187.4) * Q1 OPERATING PROFIT SEK 4.4 MILLION VERSUS SEK 48.7 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q1 NET INCOME SEK 3.3 MILLION VERSUS SEK 43.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
* “2018 WILL CLEARLY BE A YEAR OF TRANSITION AND WE EXPECT NET SALES TO BE LOWER IN THE COMING QUARTER COMPARED WITH THE YEAR-ON-YEAR PERIOD” - CEO
* “OUR AIM IS TO IMPROVE NET SALES GROWTH THROUGH CONTINUED EXPANSION OF OUR GEOGRAPHICAL REACH AND FASTER COMMERCIALIZATION OF OUR INNOVATION PORTFOLIO” - CEO Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
